      "content": "i tried talking to them, but it just makes it worse. they try to be nice and say it's fine, but i can see the stress in their eyes. they have their own lives, their own problems... and i'm just adding more to their plate every single day. i just feel like i'm taking up space that they could be using for something better. like, wouldn't it be easier for everyone if i just wasn't such a constant problem?",
